  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1556188/" class="title-link">读后感一则</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1556188"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dumplingrice/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2914111-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dumplingrice/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">无尽意处</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-11-15"
      class="main-meta">2008-11-15 14:40:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1556188_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   “纪念碑性”是巫鸿先生在研究阐释中国古代艺术史中关于礼器的社会功能、宗教政治功能时所采用的一个重要名词。在本文的第一个部分，巫鸿及就此概念进行了充分的解释，即“纪念碑性”和现代所理解的“纪念碑”在内涵上有着深刻的不同，前者与后者是“内容”和“形式”上的关系...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1556188/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1556188_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1556188_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



